<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The Hole has a lot more than just caster loot.  IMHO, the best shoulders for melee drop there, granite spaulders, one of the best arms for a druid drop there, withered leather arms, etc.<BR>
<BR>
Rangers and Shamans should be happy to know that the Paineel Steel BP drops there, which is AC 22 and looks like black plate when worn.<BR>
<BR>
My core group has recieved every piece of loam except for the robe.  Loam just plain rocks, if you ask me.  Its "attainable" to more people.  You can't just go to hate or fear and pick up some new arms or legs... but you can do this in the hole.<BR>
<BR>
Xith</font></td></tr></table>
